iintgui (0.10.0-1+deb9u5~fsec) stretch; urgency=low

  * Several improvements and feature implementations:
    + background (if present) is integrated and stored in output file
    + automatic retaining of previous settings in signal defition
    + clearer setting structure in signal definition
    + internal stuff: catch more exceptions and write log messages in window

  * Bug fixes:
    - wrong actions and options after button clicks, one re-appearing internal name mismatch
    - button resets in signal fitting after repeated bkg fits
    - clear: internal name mismatch when changing from de-spiking to non de-spiking

